Package com.filesender.HelperClasses

Package which is general set of different classes required for FileSender project to work.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    globals
    Class containing all the properties that have global usage and are used too often to put them in the local scope.
    IPAddressValidator
    Class for validating IP address correctness with regular expression.
    Log
    Class for displaying output in FileSender application.
    Operation
    Objects of this class are meant to be sent as operation indicators for server with possible arguments.
    ServerStatus
    Class for checking weather the server that we have connected to before is still available.
    ToSend
    This class is internally used by functions sending and receiving File Trees
